illage\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.785372931106133e-16, \"text\": \"Olympic Village\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\"}, {\"begin\": 1222, \"end\": 1238, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"score\": 0.9997861899246632, \"rank\": 0.00021385579854739525, \"text\": \"Associated Press\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Swimmer Tamara Potocka was seen sitting poolside for a few seconds in clear distress, even as swimmers lined up for the next heat.\", \"from\": 1241, \"to\": 1371, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1249, \"end\": 1255, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tamara_Todevska\", \"score\": 0.9840185405343354, \"rank\": 0.016045995856337675, \"text\": \"Tamara\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tamara_Todevska\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tamara_Todevska\"}, {\"begin\": 1256, \"end\": 1263, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Potocki_family\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Potocka\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Potocki_family\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Potocki_family\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Organisers realised something was wrong and postponed the next swim as medical staff descended on the scene.\", \"from\": 1373, \"to\": 1481, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Footage:https://t.co/qjVWmTpV7bpic.twitter.com/jl0y8GmbTD  - arabworld (@arabwor37664978)August 2, 2024    Upon collapsing, medical professionals raced toward Tamara and carried her away on a stretcher.\", \"from\": 1483, \"to\": 1685, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's unclear if they needed to administer CPR to the swimm