 there.\\\"\", \"from\": 2242, \"to\": 2317, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A post shared by Tamara Potocka\\u0301 (@tampot0cka)    Two days prior, Tamara shared photos of her time in the Paris Olympic Village and from the opening ceremony, posing in front of the Eiffel Tower.\", \"from\": 2321, \"to\": 2516, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2338, \"end\": 2344, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tamara_Todevska\", \"score\": 0.9840185405343354, \"rank\": 0.016045995856337675, \"text\": \"Tamara\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tamara_Todevska\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tamara_Todevska\"}, {\"begin\": 2387, \"end\": 2393, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tamara_Todevska\", \"score\": 0.9840185405343354, \"rank\": 0.016045995856337675, \"text\": \"Tamara\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tamara_Todevska\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tamara_Todevska\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"fit pt.\", \"from\": 2518, \"to\": 2526, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"2 aka getting wet at the opening ceremony of the Olympics,\\\" she captioned anInstagrampost earlier this week.\", \"from\": 2527, \"to\": 2635, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"While taking to the comments section, many of Tamara's followers sent their best wishes after they saw her collapse on television.\", \"from\": 2637, \"to\": 2767, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2683, \"end\": 2689, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tamara_Todevska\", \"score\": 0.9840185405343354, \"rank\": 0.016045995856337675, \"text\": \"Tamara\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tamara_Todevska\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tamara_Todevska\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Many others also asked, \\\"Are you ok?\\\"\", \"from\": 2768, \"to\": 2805, \"e